      "paragraphContext": "Art can be found everywhere, from museums and galleries to public spaces and even our own homes.  It shapes our identities, reflects our values, and challenges us to see the world in new ways.  Consider the different forms art takes – music, dance, literature, film – and how they contribute to our shared human experience.",
